WEBVTT

00:00.056 --> 00:02.028
<i>Previously on</i>
Beauty and the Beast...

00:02.029 --> 00:04.713
My husband was an archaeologist,
he was helping us on a case,

00:04.714 --> 00:06.580
and whatever he discovered
got him killed.

00:07.849 --> 00:09.950
London, 1836.

00:10.017 --> 00:11.253
Is that the same gem?

00:11.254 --> 00:13.321
Scotland Yard found it
at a murder scene.

00:13.322 --> 00:15.603
In fact, it's been found at
many murder scenes ever since,

00:15.624 --> 00:17.959
including one that
your father investigated.

00:18.026 --> 00:21.028
There is something about this
gem that is definitely connected

00:21.096 --> 00:22.896
to you, Catherine.

00:22.965 --> 00:25.232
It's a beast collar.

00:25.300 --> 00:26.700
A collar?

00:26.768 --> 00:29.903
Which implies somebody
was controlling it.

00:29.972 --> 00:33.074
Why would someone want a gem
that controls beasts?

00:33.141 --> 00:34.308
You have to get it back.

00:34.376 --> 00:36.477
No, we do.

00:43.384 --> 00:45.318
Well, you know
what's not fair?

00:45.386 --> 00:47.320
What, that my mother
didn't teach me how to cook?

00:47.388 --> 00:48.889
No.

00:48.957 --> 00:50.757
I agree to take a
celebrity cooking class

00:50.825 --> 00:52.058
hoping to get
some action...

00:52.126 --> 00:53.460
Tess, shh!
No!

00:53.528 --> 00:56.162
And you are like catnip
to every single guy.

00:56.230 --> 00:57.663
Including Chef Raymond.

00:57.731 --> 01:00.566
Okay, no more vino for you.
It's not fair.

01:00.634 --> 01:02.602
Okay, it's not my fault. I
didn't realize this was gonna be

01:02.669 --> 01:05.471
an aphrodisiac theme when
I was the one to host the class.

01:05.539 --> 01:08.441
I just hope that my canapes
don't make JT's party into...

01:08.509 --> 01:10.276
An orgy?

01:10.344 --> 01:11.978
I was going
to say disaster.

01:12.045 --> 01:13.679
You need to eat something.

01:13.747 --> 01:15.014
Not oysters.

01:15.081 --> 01:16.281
How's it going over here?

01:16.349 --> 01:17.850
Good.
Good! You know,

01:17.918 --> 01:19.952
as long as my canapes
don't go up in flames.

01:20.020 --> 01:21.353
Flambé.

01:21.421 --> 01:23.022
Mm.
It's also an aphrodisiac.

01:27.494 --> 01:29.461
I've been single too long.
Guys can sense it.

01:29.529 --> 01:31.430
No, they can't.
Yes, they can.

01:31.498 --> 01:33.332
It's a proven fact.

01:33.400 --> 01:35.501
Okay, it's anecdotal,
but it's true, all right?

01:35.568 --> 01:36.868
They don't...
they don't like desperate,

01:36.936 --> 01:38.504
and they don't like to wait.

01:38.571 --> 01:39.804
Like Gabe, for example.

01:39.872 --> 01:41.340
What do you mean,
"like Gabe"?

01:41.408 --> 01:44.142
Well, you know
he's leaving, right?

01:44.209 --> 01:46.511
Not, like, for good.
He's just leaving the precinct.

01:46.579 --> 01:49.014
He didn't tell you?

01:49.081 --> 01:50.281
No, he didn't.

01:50.349 --> 01:51.282
Why is he leaving?

01:51.350 --> 01:52.784
Well, his work is done.

01:52.852 --> 01:54.853
He cleaned up Joe's mess,
he arrested your dad.

01:54.921 --> 01:56.855
Now the D.O.J.'s
bringing it back to command.

01:56.923 --> 01:58.222
Like I said, guys don't wait.

01:58.290 --> 01:59.858
Tess, I am not
going to get

01:59.926 --> 02:01.125
into a relationship
so soon.

02:01.193 --> 02:02.360
Hey, if you don't like him...

02:02.428 --> 02:03.827
No, I-I like him,
it's just...

02:03.895 --> 02:06.330
Look, Cat, I'm all for
self-discovery, okay?

02:06.398 --> 02:08.466
God knows I'm the queen
of it right now.

02:08.533 --> 02:09.833
But it...

02:09.901 --> 02:11.222
it doesn't keep you
warm at night.

02:11.270 --> 02:12.503
And it doesn't
curl your toes.

02:12.571 --> 02:14.705
Curl my toes?

02:14.773 --> 02:16.541
I'm just saying,
use it or lose it.

02:18.610 --> 02:20.143
Hey, is everything
all right?

02:20.211 --> 02:21.745
You know what?
I'm not sure.

02:21.813 --> 02:23.681
Uh, am I calling too late?

02:23.748 --> 02:25.716
No, I'm, uh... I'm just cooking.

02:25.784 --> 02:27.417
Cooking? Really?

02:27.485 --> 02:30.020
Okay, be nice.

02:30.088 --> 02:31.521
Any sign of Agent Landon?

02:31.590 --> 02:33.223
No.

02:33.291 --> 02:35.692
No, and that's what worries me.

02:35.759 --> 02:37.727
You know, I know she's, uh,
suspicious of Tori

02:37.795 --> 02:39.162
and, you know, maybe me, too.

02:39.230 --> 02:41.198
She knows
something strange happened

02:41.265 --> 02:43.166
and she knows that
we're hiding it from her.

02:43.234 --> 02:45.435
If she finds out,
then I'm exposed

02:45.503 --> 02:47.204
and you are
completely screwed.

02:47.271 --> 02:49.706
Yeah, but I still think that
if we can figure out who killed

02:49.773 --> 02:51.774
her husband all those years ago,
maybe she'll go away.

02:51.842 --> 02:53.876
You know, I know
if we find the stolen gem,

02:53.944 --> 02:55.411
then we will find the killer.

02:55.479 --> 02:57.947
Okay, but how do we find
the gem?

02:58.015 --> 02:59.215
Well,

02:59.282 --> 03:01.417
same way that your ancestor did.

03:01.485 --> 03:05.588
Rebecca followed the same gem
when it was stolen back in 1840

03:05.656 --> 03:08.257
to get this:

03:08.325 --> 03:12.027
"a dark, gothic dungeon
filled with a treasure trove

03:12.095 --> 03:14.430
of artifacts...
and creature-like skeletons."

03:14.498 --> 03:17.266
A dungeon? In Manhattan?

03:17.334 --> 03:18.367
Apparently.

03:18.435 --> 03:19.935
Now, the problem is

03:20.003 --> 03:21.537
it's in a part of the city

03:21.605 --> 03:23.605
that doesn't exist anymore
on any map.

03:23.673 --> 03:26.274
Okay, but why would
whoever took this gem

03:26.342 --> 03:28.143
be holing themselves
up there now?

03:28.210 --> 03:30.311
Well, because it's full of
these unique artifacts

03:30.379 --> 03:33.314
that this guy's been
stealing for years, right?

03:33.382 --> 03:35.216
Besides, what better way
to hide from the FBI

03:35.284 --> 03:37.585
than a place that is
impossible to find?

03:37.654 --> 03:39.621
I don't know,
it's sounds like a long shot.

03:39.688 --> 03:42.790
Well, it's the only
shot we got.

03:42.858 --> 03:44.592
Look, Catherine,

03:44.660 --> 03:46.894
right or wrong,
I have chosen a completely

03:46.962 --> 03:48.229
different path than you.

03:48.297 --> 03:50.165
Which means as soon as
we solve this,

03:50.232 --> 03:51.832
you can finally go back
to your own life

03:51.900 --> 03:53.301
and get away
from all of this.

03:53.369 --> 03:55.936
Vincent, we've had
this conversation.

03:56.004 --> 03:57.964
Because of Rebecca,
this is as much about me as...

03:59.340 --> 04:00.775
Hey, what's going on?
You okay?

04:00.842 --> 04:02.843
Flambé. I got to go.

04:04.546 --> 04:06.147
Who was that?

04:08.216 --> 04:11.152
Catherine?

04:11.219 --> 04:13.253
Yeah.

04:13.321 --> 04:14.488
Again.

04:14.556 --> 04:16.122
"Again?" Tori, come on.
"Come on," what?

04:16.190 --> 04:17.257
You talk to her every day.

04:17.325 --> 04:18.757
What am I supposed to think?

04:18.826 --> 04:20.927
That we're trying
to get the FBI off our backs.

04:20.995 --> 04:22.095
Okay? That's what.

04:22.163 --> 04:23.263
It's not her back that we have

04:23.331 --> 04:24.598
to worry about, it's ours.

04:24.666 --> 04:26.667
That gem can hurt us,
not Catherine.

04:26.734 --> 04:28.202
Well, Agent Landon
can hurt Catherine, okay,

04:28.269 --> 04:30.369
a lot for trying to
cover this up, all right?

04:30.437 --> 04:32.305
She's just
trying to help us.

04:32.372 --> 04:34.340
She's not helping us,

04:34.408 --> 04:36.042
she's helping
you, Vincent.

04:37.511 --> 04:39.012
Listen, I'm...

04:39.080 --> 04:41.815
I'm sorry.

04:41.882 --> 04:43.683
I don't know,
I guess I'm just nervous.

04:43.751 --> 04:47.520
I know you never
promised me a future, but...

04:47.588 --> 04:52.291
we have been in some
kind of relationship, and...

04:52.359 --> 04:55.794
I guess I was just
hoping that...

04:55.862 --> 05:00.299
you'd stop sneaking out of bed
every night to call her.

05:00.367 --> 05:02.134
Okay, I'm sorry.

05:02.202 --> 05:04.002
What do you
want me to say?

05:04.070 --> 05:06.138
That you don't want
to go back to her.

05:09.575 --> 05:10.876
Do you?
You know, right now,

05:10.944 --> 05:12.510
all I want is
to find out

05:12.578 --> 05:14.813
whoever has that damn gem
and stop them before

05:14.881 --> 05:16.815
Agent Landon finds out
what's really going on.

